- Headings: 20–28px, weight 600–700
- Card titles: 14–16px, weight 500–600
- Body: 12–14px, weight 400
- Microcopy: 11–12px, weight 300–400
- Spacing: 8px baseline grid; gutters 220–260px; header 56–64px; card padding 16–20px
- Alignment: left-aligned lists; mixed layout for main content; dense vertical spacing in trees/lists

Key Design Elements
- Card: dark, elevated, rounded 8–12px; gradient background; inner top highlight
- Navigation: left vertical with active accent pill; collapsible sections
- Data Visualization: minimal charts with subdued grids and colored series
- Interactive Elements: primary/secondary buttons, inputs, toggles, chips, micro-interactions
- Badges: counts and alerts with appropriate color usage

Connected Pages
- Master Dashboard: Global search, quick command bar, cronjobs snapshot, cross-module alerts, quick-access workflows.

